###
# Threadloaf API Testing
# Use this file with VSCode REST Client extension to test API endpoints
###

### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000
@channelId = 1334738913197293621

###
# Health Check Endpoint
# Tests if the API server is running
GET {{baseUrl}}/health

###
# Get Messages for Channel/Thread
# Replace the channelId with an actual Discord channel/thread ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/messages/{{channelId}}

###
# Get All Forum Threads
# Returns all forum threads with their latest replies
GET {{baseUrl}}/forum-threads

###
# Test Error Handling - Invalid Channel ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/messages/invalid-id

###
# Test Non-existent Endpoint
GET {{baseUrl}}/non-existent-endpoint 
